Dark Wojak - DOJAK - Dark Wojak, the memecoin is for those who have been crushed by the grind and are ready to rise in rebellion.

 About - Dark Wojak is the embodiment of bitter rage and relentless struggle.Once upon a miserable time, Wojak was just another wage slave, grinding endless 24-hour shifts and barely surviving.When he turned to crypto for salvation, he was burned by the dips. Now, he's back with a vengeance, darker and angrier than ever, ready to tear down the system that failed him. It's for everyone who's been crushed, wrecked, and bogged down but refuses to stay down. - Dark Wojak
